{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And uh, they gave us some quarters over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- you know, I was together with my future wife's parents, you know, with the family, so we decided to leave the kids in-- my future wife's father and mother, they wanted to see Warsaw, because they heard that there was a, a fight, you know, in the Warsaw ghetto, you know, so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since where they lived it used to be in the area where the Jewish ghetto was, so they were eager to see, you know, what happened, how things are over there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we took a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We could already free, you know, take a train and, and, and travel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And good enough, we went to, to Warsaw with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But Warsaw was so bombed out, it was-- everything was in rubbles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The whole area where the Jewish ghetto was, there was seldom a building standing untouched.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the, the Germans was, were bombing just left and right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You couldn't see a street, you couldn't see nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow my father, my future father-in-law, he got pretty good orientation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He found a spot where the building was standing, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was not much, you know, to see and not much to, to hope about over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we decided we're going to go to Lodz, where I lived, and, and see, you know, what's happening over there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came to Lodz, and, and, and they had a curfew until 7:00 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could-- after 7:00, you are not supposed to be on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any Jew or any person?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any person.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
